title: Changing How You Think About Your Past to Lose Weight
itunes:title: Changing How You Think About Your Past to Lose Weight
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

Many of us have pasts we would rather forget. Every day it's lurking around in our head driving us to eat. Today we teach you how to put the past behind you and drop the ways you blame that bully in 6th grade, the ex-husband, and more for your overeating today.
